original_title: Adam Carolla: Not Taco Bell Material
overview: Not Taco Bell Material is Adam Carolla’s first ever stand up special based on his New York Times best-selling autobiography. The performance showcases Adam’s incredible improvisational comedy skills featuring tales from his youth, told through stand-up comedy and photos. It’s hilarious, poignant, and even inspiring.
title: Adam Carolla: Not Taco Bell Material
